:File
File

Provides a menu of File options for saving the 
contents of the text window.

The choices include saving to the file
currently associated with this window, saving 
the contents in a new file, and others.

:View
View

Provides ways to change the position of the
cursor and the way lines are wrapped.

Defaults to Select Line at Number or the
most recently selected option on the menu.

:Edit
Edit

Provides a menu of Edit options including 
Copy, Cut, Paste, Undo, and others.

Defaults to Again or the most
recently selected option on the menu.

:Find
Find

Provides a menu of options for finding and 
replacing text.  

:Panel

This is the control panel for the 
Text Editor program.
